`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Remove_Curse
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'remove curse' <character>
 * cast 'remove curse' <object>

 This spell removes a curse from a character, and might possibly uncurse a
cursed object.	It may also be targeted on an object in the caster's inventory,
in which case its chance of success is significantly higher.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
